title: The Slipperiest Champion in League Of Legends (IT'S NOT FIZZ)

embed.description: Who would've thought the slipperiest champion of league of legends would be played by the real mr4eva. Gotta wonder why no one appreciates my value as bard support. Like really, doesn't playing some sweet melodies your adc? In the short perhaps guitar is more important than your gameplay mechanics in LoL.

replies.body: This hurts my ears, it sounds very snarky.
